Package: agronomy
Type: Package
Title: Calculation of Fertilizer Dose, Seed Rate, and Herbicide Rate
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sagar Kafle <sagar_kafle@outlook.com>
Maintainer: Sagar Kafle <sagar_kafle@outlook.com>
Description: The "agronomy" package is a collection of R functions that allow users to easily calculate fertilizer doses, amount of seed for sowing, and herbicide application rates. These functions take into account various factors such as the area of land to be treated, the nutrient content of different fertilizers, and the desired plant population or weed control. With the help of this package, farmers, students and agricultural researchers can make informed decisions about crop management.
